question.title: Will a member of the Trump family be the Republican nominee for the US Presidency in 2024?
question.body:
Resolves **Yes** if one of these individuals is the Republican nominee for the US Presidency in 2024:

 - Donald Trump
 - Donald Trump Jr.
 - Eric Trump
 - Ivanka Trump
 - Tiffany Trump
 - Melania Trump
 - Barron Trump

question.title: Will a Trump family member secure the Republican nomination for the 2024 US Presidential election?
question.body:
The question resolves to **Yes** if any of the following individuals becomes the Republican nominee for the US Presidency in 2024:

 - Donald Trump
 - Donald Trump Jr.
 - Eric Trump
 - Ivanka Trump
 - Tiffany Trump
 - Melania Trump
 - Barron Trump

question.title: Will Donald Trump be the Republican nominee for the 2024 US Presidential Election?
question.body:
This question will resolve as **Yes** if Donald Trump is selected by the Republican National Convention as the nominee for the 2024 US Presidential Election. All other candidates will resolve as **No**. This question may consider new candidates added in the future.

For this question, it is not relevant who receives the Republican nomination on the day of the 2024 US election; it is solely determined by who is selected by the delegates of the [Republican National Convention](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Republican_National_Convention).

question.title: Will Donald Trump secure the Republican nomination for the 2024 Presidential Election in the United States?
question.body:
This inquiry will conclude with a **Yes** if Donald Trump is chosen by the Republican National Convention as the nominee for the 2024 Presidential Election in the United States. Any other candidate will result in a **No**. This question may include new candidates introduced in the future.

For this question, the relevant factor is not who holds the Republican nomination on the day of the 2024 US election; it is exclusively about who is selected by the delegates at the [Republican National Convention](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Republican_National_Convention).

question.title: Is Tucker Carlson going to be chosen as the Republican candidate for the 2024 US Presidential Election?
question.body:
This question will be answered with a **Yes** if Tucker Carlson is picked by the Republican National Convention as the candidate for the 2024 US Presidential Election. If any other individual is chosen, the answer will be **No**. The question is open to candidates beyond those currently mentioned; additional candidates might be included later.

It is irrelevant for this question who is the Republican nominee on the date of the 2024 US election; it is only about who the delegates of the [Republican National Convention](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Republican_National_Convention) select.
